AniGame BOT 22-Jul-20 03:37 AM
Command: tr
Adds the things that you need once you have initiated a trade through .trade @user! If something goes wrong, do .tr cancel to cancel the trade. If the trade is complete, do .tr confirm to confirm the trade from both parties.
tr add [attr=gold] [num=0]
Adds stuff to the trade!
tr cancel
Cancels the trade if something goes wrong. Note that this command can be used by someone that's not currently within the trade.
tr confirm
Confirms the trade, has to be done by both parties.
tr view
Shows you what exactly is in the trade. If there's too many cards in the trade, it might not show properly.
Use ahelp <command or command group, case sensitive> for more info on a command.

tr add [attr=gold] [num=0]
Adds stuff to the trade!
tr cancel
Cancels the trade if something goes wrong. Note that this command can be used by someone that's not currently within the trade.
tr confirm
Confirms the trade, has to be done by both parties.
tr view
Shows you what exactly is in the trade. If there's too many cards in the trade, it might not show properly.
Use ahelp <command or command group, case sensitive> for more info on a command.
